    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-associations bg-white py-12 md:py-16 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-8\">\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: associations-eyebrow | Replace with the practice's professional memberships label. -->\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-associations-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans text-gray-400\">\n        Professional Memberships &amp; Affiliations\n      </span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16\">\n      <!-- AI-IMAGE: associations-logo-1 | Replace with the practice's first association logo. -->\n      <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-associations-component-logo-1 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-70 hover:scale-105\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/200/80?random=20\" alt=\"American Dental Association\" class=\"h-16 w-auto object-contain\" />\n      </a>\n      <!-- AI-IMAGE: associations-logo-2 | Replace with the practice's second association logo. -->\n      <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-associations-component-logo-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-70 hover:scale-105\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/200/80?random=21\" alt=\"State Dental Association\" class=\"h-16 w-auto object-contain\" />\n      </a>\n      <!-- AI-IMAGE: associations-logo-3 | Replace with the practice's third association logo. -->\n      <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-associations-component-logo-3 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-70 hover:scale-105\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/200/80?random=22\" alt=\"Academy of General Dentistry\" class=\"h-16 w-auto object-contain\" />\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
